{"tid":2099161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國退出世衛 拜登：我任期「第一天」就回鍋","createTime":"2020-07-08T04:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T21:19:56.000Z","uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f979144ce4e377ac3ac2c473efec7f98d06d547c","tid":2099161,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國正式告知聯合國秘書長古特瑞斯（Antonio Guterres），將於明年7月6日生效退出世界衛生組織（WHO），但美民主黨總統候選人拜登表示，若成功當選，將於任期第一天讓美國重返世衛。<br />\n<br />\n《法廣》報導，美國總統川普在這次的武漢肺炎疫情中，對於世界衛生組織的作法相當不滿，並在今年5月底稱「終止與世界衛生組織的關係」，批評中國在世衛中有絕對優勢的地位，且世衛沒有進行實質性改革，美國國務院發言人今天表示，美國已正式告知聯合國秘書長古特瑞斯（Antonio Guterres）將退出世界衛生組織（WHO），並於明年7月6日生效。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，美國參議院外交委員會民主黨籍首席議員梅南德茲（Robert Menendez）批評，川普退出世衛之舉無法保護美國人民，反而使美國孤立，民主黨總統候選人拜登則說，若選舉成功，他將在總統任期的第一天宣布美國重回世界衛生組織。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3221270?utm_medium=R&amp;utm_campaign=SHARE&amp;utm_source=FACEBOOK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3221270%3Futm_medium%3DR%26utm_campaign%3DSHARE%26utm_source%3DFACEBOOK&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDKwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=4b81e697\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3221270%3Futm_medium%3DR%26utm_campaign%3DSHARE%26utm_source%3DFACEBOOK&h=902c1fe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3221270?utm_medium=R&amp;utm_campaign=SHARE&amp;utm_source=FACEBOOK</a>"},{"pid":"0ad04b29c5cb17458411218d905e036681442cba","tid":2099161,"uid":176313,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:38:31.000Z","msg":"佢上就真係死得&hellip;"},{"pid":"45011068517bc5250ca9fafff9aa86ef78df56cd","tid":2099161,"uid":123738,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"仲想奶黑鬼屎眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚佢一天都無"},{"pid":"3f73